faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人唔好干涉英國內政啦<br />\n尋日事頭婆同BoJo一著 英國硬脫歐架啦<br />\n<br />\n中立少少講 要知既係<br />\n留歐派同香港示威者夾既 的確比較多人崇尚自由民主普世價值 左膠呀嘛 你當係香港既民主黨lor<br />\n脫歐派同香港人夾既 咪支持強大英國 反對移民同人口跨境流動 <br />\n你當佢地係嗌緊「光復英國 時代革命」 不過係老人家嗌咁解 唔比英國老人家有智慧想守住英國傳統文化既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以左膠會覺得班老人家係廢老 阻住佢地同伊斯蘭世界同中國人做朋友"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T04:14:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a46f9e3089d1b61d18cf3ea03f8cc10937758bc2","tid":1514833,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T04:59:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49e1ea89b2410373aba4c8b6eb070b968a903445","tid":1514833,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T05:15:05.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eea1988ec23639850864b8551e76cd45b8f7928c","tid":1514833,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T07:11:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06352778d8067dc9c01e0a9db5524d2c6d8e085b","tid":1514833,"uid":205682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T07:12:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"41d0d2a12b72990d322f37e1b492e64df1a71080","tid":1514833,"uid":189652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T07:12:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a1b169a5068d5848de3377198659d46f815b85e7","tid":1514833,"uid":131122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T07:14:29.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29be225bcbd9cadbbad00cb0d1bd108c77650b2c","tid":1514833,"uid":20285,"like":0,"d